reviews.text:
So finally cracked this open. Been wanting to try this since its release and well yeah... &#xD;
A fantastic mix by nick. I ended up subbing for MB's strawberry milk but this is a great strawberry with a thick dairy milky mid note that rides throughout with lovely lashings of vanilla. &#xD;
Cheers nick, this ones staying in rotation buddy. Might be worth making this a oneshot 👊👊👊👊
